Due Date: Regular maintenance on CSTR reactor system
Inspect distillation column internals and packing
Perform integrity testing on chemical storage tanks
Replace worn pump seals on process pumps
Calibrate gas chromatograph and pH meters
Test and inspect emergency safety showers
Maintain wet scrubber system and replace packing
Test emergency generator and check fuel system
Calibrate temperature sensors on batch reactor
Inspect vacuum system on distillation column
Replace faulty level sensors on storage tanks
Change oil and filters on process air compressor
Inspect all safety equipment and eyewash stations
Update control system software and test
